beer.beer_description:
Check out BERRY SAZY - this juicy little number is perfect for the warming (no really) weather.

We started with the malt base from our Caribbean Fog hazy pale, added bucket loads of raspberry, strawberry and boysenberry, and soured it.

The result is a smooth, refreshing and berry fruity sour with a lovely colour to boot.
